data.description: Step into luxury living with this stunning 5 bedroom, 2.5 bath residence boasting exquisite details and modern amenities. Wood floors grace the main living areas, enhancing the elegant ambiance throughout. The living room  and great room feature a cozy double sided fireplace, perfect for gatherings. The spacious kitchen offers a breakfast bar and overlooks a charming breakfast sitting area, complete with a pantry for added convenience. Upstairs, discover 5 generously sized bedrooms. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, boasting tray ceilings and a large ensuite bathroom with dual sinks, a garden tub, and a separate shower. Outside, a large fenced yard with a patio beckons for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. Plus, enjoy the fantastic amenities of the community, including a clubhouse, pool, playground, tennis courts, and a sport court. Don't miss the opportunity to call this remarkable property home, where luxury and convenience await at every turn!
